 261:          | OOO | <-Pair-> |OOO  |  |  why NE, E, SE, S are missing.
 262:          | OOO |          |OOO  |  |
 263:          |     |          |     |  |  Take for example

 269:          |     |          |     |  |  +-----+ Moving Point O to the right,
 270:          | OOO |   SWest  |     |  |  | GGG |
